#: src/server.py:6679 src/server.py:6697
msgid ""
"This feature depends heavily on the quality of your model and sufficient "
"lighting conditions."
msgstr ""

#: src/server.py:6680
msgid ""
"If one or both are not good, the detection may either fail or other - "
"similiar looking cats may be detected as your cat."
